signup_confirm_email.message:
You (or someone else) entered this email address when creating an account at {{global:site_name}}.

If you did not create an account, you can ignore this message.

To confirm your email, please proceed to
 {{global:site_url}}#/sign/confirm/{{args:hash}}

or enter {{args:hash}} when requested after login.{{global:signature}}{{global:footer}}

password_reset_request.message:
You (or someone else) entered this email address when trying to change the password of your {{global:site_name}} account.

If you did not request this, someone else may have access to your email account. We recommend you change your {{global:site_name}} account password to be safe.

To continue the password reset process, please proceed to
 {{global:site_url}}#/sign/password/{{args:hash}}
 within 60 minutes of receiving this email.{{global:signature}}{{global:footer}}

password_reset_request_new.message:
Hopefully this email doesn't come as a surprise.  An account has just been created for you by {{from:user_name_first}} at {{global:site_name}}.

To complete your account, proceed to
 {{global:site_url}}#/sign/password/{{args:hash}}{{global:signature}}{{global:footer}}

email_changed_notification.message:
Your {{global:site_name}} account email was just changed.

To confirm your email, please proceed to
 {{global:site_url}}#/sign/confirm/{{args:hash}}{{global:footer}}
